msgid ""
msgstr "The number to start numbering channels from. Only used when [B]Use backend channel numbers[/B] from PVR settings is enabled and a channel number is not supplied in the M3U file."

#. help: Channels - oneRadioGroup
#. help: Channels - twoRadioGroup
#. help: Channels - threeRadioGroup
